Package: trees3D
Type: Package
Title: Visualizing a single or stand of trees in 3D using openGL
Version: 1.0
Date: 2016
Author: Daniel Falster and Remko Duursma
Depends:
    R (>= 3.0.0)
Maintainer: Daniel Falster <daniel.falster@mq.edu.au>
Description: Using the openGL library generate 3D plots of a stand of trees, given crown
